item.title: Here we have a few of the pieds we recently hatched out! This morph is easily recognized by its large white blotches! Although some have very little white! Such an amazing morph!

item.title: I think our ugly egg is getting uglier. I hope it can make it another 30 days!

item.title: Feeding our new tarantula!
item.description: This little one is brand new to me, so it hasn't had the chance to really settle in. But I was feeding all of my tarantulas, so I figured I would give it a go. I left the cricket in there for a bit and nothing. We will try again after it settles in.

item.title: Do you think I made the right call?
